widgets_values:
flux checkpoint + loras 
by: pkeffect

Main Flux models/checkpoints
- flux.1-dev.safetensors 
https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/resolve/main/flux1-dev.safetensors

- flux.1-schnell.safetensors
https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/resolve/main/flux1-schnell.safetensors

Put them in directory: 
- ComfyUI/models/unet/

You will need these three files: 
- clip_l.safetensors
- t5xxl_fp16.safetensors
- t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors 

Downloaded them all from here:
- https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main

All three of the above files go in the directory:
- ComfyUI/models/clip/

Also:
- ae.safetensors
Downloaded from here:
https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/resolve/main/ae.safetensors

Put in directory: 
- ComfyUI/models/vae/

nodes.title: Notes
widgets_values:
flux gguf + loras 
by: pkeffect

This is for gguf quantized models only!

Download from here or search for your own:
https://huggingface.co/city96/FLUX.1-dev-gguf/tree/main

Put them in directory: 
- ComfyUI/models/unet/

You will need these three files: 
- clip_l.safetensors
- t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors 

Downloaded them all from here:
- https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main

All three of the above files go in the directory:
- ComfyUI/models/clip/

Also:
- ae.safetensors
Downloaded from here:
https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/resolve/main/ae.safetensors

Put in directory: 
- ComfyUI/models/vae/
